This pair of classic blue capris by Levis sports a trendy look for the women who love fashion. This pair of regular fit cotton capris has two insert pockets on its front with an insert pocket in the right one and two patch pockets on its back donning embroidered detailing. To complete with it has got a metal zipper as well as a button closure on the front.Style Tips
  • For a casual look pair with a white shirt and smart shoes.
  • It will look great when teamed up with a smart T-shirt for a chic look.
Material & Care
  • Made of denim.
  • Turn them inside out before washing.
  • Wash in cold water or hand wash.
  • Line dry.
